            </p>
            <p style="max-width: 200px;margin:0 auto;">
                <a class="pure-button pure-button-primary" id="downloadfile" style="width: 200px;text-align: center;padding: 15px 0px;" href="#">下载Epoint.PingBiao1.5</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
